description:
Join MauLer, Nerdrotic, Reaper, Outcasts Creative and yours truly as we review the two big releases this week - Fallout and Civil War. Plus the ongoing battle to keep Warhammer safe from The Message. And the hilarious news that Lucasfilm STILL hasn't made back their purchase price for Disney. 

Subscribe to Nerdrotic: https://www.youtube.com/@nerdrotic
Subscribe to Reaper: https://www.youtube.com/@RealReaper
Subscribe to Outcasts Creative: https://www.youtube.com/@THEOUTCASTSCREATIVE
Outcast's Book: https://www.amazon.com/1988-Journal-love-films-friendship/dp/B0C6C7B6HR
title: Open Bar #91 - The Fallout of Civil War, Lucasfilm Strikes Out, The War for Warhammer
